Package: mapboxapi
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to 'Mapbox' Web Services
Date: 2020-09-25
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Kyle", family = "Walker", email = "kyle@walker-data.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Kyle Walker <kyle@walker-data.com>
Description: An R interface to 'Mapbox' web services and the 'tippecanoe' tile-generation utility.
  The package includes support for 'Mapbox' Navigation APIs, including directions, isochrones,
  and route optimization; the Search API for forward and reverse geocoding; and the Maps API for 
  interacting with 'Mapbox' vector tilesets and visualizing 'Mapbox' maps in R.  See
  <https://docs.mapbox.com/api/> for more information about the 'Mapbox' APIs.
